        "Tafseer": "\"Or is theirs the sovereignty of the heavens and the earth and what is between them? Then let them ascend through [any] ways.\" (10)\n\nThis is a further detail of the preceding verse. That is, if their assumption is that the sovereignty of the heavens and the earth is in their hands, then let them ascend to the heavens and block the mercy which Allah Almighty is sending down upon His servant.\n\n'Asbab' refers to 'Asbab as-samawat' (the ways of the heavens). This word is also used in the sense of the horizons and attachments of something. Its analysis has passed in its proper place."
