    {
        "SurahNumber": 38,
        "AyahNumber": 52,
        "Tafseer": "\"And with them will be women limiting [their] glances, of equal age.\" (52)\n\n'Qasirat-ut-Tarf' refers to modest and شرمیلی beauties. With the Arabs and all people of honor, the highest attribute of a woman has been considered to be this. 'Atrab' means of equal age—meaning for the completion of their joy, modest and equal-aged beauties will be by their side.\n\n'This is what you are promised...'—giving these blessings, they will be told: 'The blessings of which you were given glad tidings for today are present here. Allah has fulfilled His promise. Whatever you have received will continuously increase. There is no fear of its ending.'"
