        "Tafseer": "\"Say, 'It is great news, From which you are turning away.'\" (67-68)\n\nThat is, warn them: 'The thing of which I am warning you is no ordinary matter, but a highly great event, yet you are indifferent to it and are mocking my warnings.'"
