    {
        "SurahNumber": 38,
        "AyahNumber": 82,
        "Tafseer": "\"[Iblis] said, 'By your might, I will surely mislead them all Except, among them, Your chosen servants.'\" (82-83)\n\nWhen he received this respite, he said with great pomp, swearing by the might and majesty of Allah: 'Now, I will surely mislead them all, and except those among them whom You choose for Your worship, all will be caught in my trap of deviation.' That is: 'I will prove that this human whom You have considered worthy of honor and dignity is not worthy of it, and I am entirely justified in not prostrating to him.'"
