    {
        "SurahNumber": 38,
        "AyahNumber": 84,
        "Tafseer": "\"[Allah] said, 'The truth [is My oath], and the truth I say - [That] I will surely fill Hell with you and those of them that follow you all together.'\" (84-85)\n\nIblis had challenged with great pomp. Allah Almighty replied to him with full majesty and complete self-sufficiency—stating: 'If you will mislead them all, then hear My true word—and I always say the truth—that I will surely fill Hell with you and those among them who follow you.'\n\nThis story is narrated to the leaders of the Quraysh and those who are blindly following them so that they also see and hear their fate in this story, if they possess eyes and ears."
